Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感觉就跟梦一样\NFelt like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}发生什么了\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你哭了  然后...\NYou cried and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我抱着你  你就睡过去了\NI held you, and you fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后我们就这样了\NAnd here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们就这样了\NHere we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想出去\NI don't want to go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不用出去  现在不用\NYou don't have to -- not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是终究得出去\NBut eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}终究得出去\NEventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以前常梦到早晨的阳光\NI used to dream about the morning sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}梦中阳光渗过指尖\NI'd run my hand through it in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是这样\NLike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在是真的了\NAnd now it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我该满心欢喜才是\NI should be filled with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要走了\NI'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也是\NMe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道去哪里吗\NDo you know where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你呢\NDo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}昭雪\N第二季第十集[季终]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托妮\NTawney?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你收到后一定给我回电话\NPlease call me when you get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让我知道你没事\NGot to let me know you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给我留个言就行  好吗  我不会回复\NJust leave a message, all right? I won't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就从冰箱里拿东西\NI just grabbed things from the refrigerator,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一边哭  一边往包里塞东西\Ncrying and... dumping stuff in a bag --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我带走一个  留一个给小泰\N"I'll take one, I'll leave Teddy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我带走一个  留一个给小泰\NI'll take one, I'll leave Teddy one."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我当时就只想着  我得吃东西啊\NMy overriding thought was, "I have to have food."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真是太不理性了\NThat's not rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也可能是太理性了\NMaybe it's too rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那种压力之下  不同的人\NDifferent people do different things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会做不同的事\Nunder that kind of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我明显是储藏食物\NI evidently hoard food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得这次野餐我们不需要搅打奶油了\NI don't think we need the whipping cream at this picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟你带的玉米片一起吃怎么样\NMaybe on your corn chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这主意我没想到\NWell, I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们就试试吧\NLet's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}咸咸的  甜甜的  脆脆的\NThe salty, the sweet, the crunch --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实也不难吃\NIt's actually not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-真的吗  -假的  很难吃\N- Really? - No, it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我饿了\NUh, I was hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吃点东西对你有好处\NIt's good for you to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}应该吧\NI guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我拿走了\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我如此习惯他  对我生气\NI was so used to him... being mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从未见他如此脆弱...\NI'd never seen him so broken-down like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如此崩溃\NSo shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你签了协议是不是就再也不能回来了\NYou can never come back here if you sign those papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}代价太高了  丹尼尔\NSuch a price to pay, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不高\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么了  丹尼尔\NWhat is it, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你离开前...\NBefore you leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在你决定未来的生活之前\NBefore you decide what your life may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要告诉你件事  托妮\NI need to tell you something, Tawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是关于小泰的\NIt's about Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他最近遇到了很多事\NHe's been dealing with a lot lately --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不知道的事\NThings you don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道吗\NAnd -- and you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}洗礼之后\NAfter the baptism,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他让我远离你\Nhe told me to stay away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是你丈夫  我知道他这么做是对的\NHe was your husband, and I know he was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也告诉他我会远离你\NAnd I told him I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后他还说了些别的事\NThen he said some other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么事\NWhat things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是  一堆话而已\NJust words... lined up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以前都听过\NI've heard them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}反正都差不多\NSimilar, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虽然还是那些话  但他很担心\NThey're just words, but he was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他担心会失去你\NHe was afraid of losing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但当时我没看出来\NBut I couldn't see that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我伤害了他  侮辱了他\NI hurt him... humiliated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是我在监狱中学的\NSomething I learned in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以让一个男人觉得  无助\NSomething to make a man feel...powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那不是强奸\NIt wasn't rape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但却很暴力\NBut it was violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且...\NAnd...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且什么\NAnd what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会让人发疯\NUnhinged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望时光能倒流\NI wish I could go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为他不该受此侮辱\NBecause he didn't deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不该带着那种烦扰度过余生\NAnd he doesn't deserve to have to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他什么都没说\NHe never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一直以为是因为我\NI always thought it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小泰\NHey, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}妈妈\NHey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在忙活店里的账本\NJust doing the books for the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你  我知道很麻烦\NWell, we appreciate it. I-I know that can be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}哪有\NNot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不要告诉泰德  不过我还挺想让他知道的\NDon't tell Ted, but I kind of look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}话说你今早来有什么事吗\NSo, what brings you here this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丹尼尔在吗\NUh, is Daniel around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他昨晚没回家\NWell, he didn't come in last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道  小泰\NI know, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过他现在正处在\NIt's just where he is right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人生的关键时期\Nyou know, in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从某种程度上说他就像个孩子\NHe's like an adolescent in some ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就应该让他去体会吧\NJust got to let him go through it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NI guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他现在可能在阿曼莎那里\NHe -- he might be at Amantha's by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}乔恩好像要跟他谈几件事\NI think Jon had to talk over a few things with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他要接受认罪协议吗\NSo, is he gonna take the plea deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道  亲爱的\NI don't know, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道他不想回监狱了\NI know he doesn't want to go back to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他已经在考虑搬走了\NHe's already talking about moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}搬去哪里\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不清楚  反正要离开波利\NI'm not sure. Away from Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切都发生得太快了\NIt's all happening so quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小泰\NTeddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的手怎么回事\NWhat's happened to your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没注意\NI, uh... I-I got distracted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}被门夹了\Nand got it caught in a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事  没事\NOh, it's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小泰  你还好吗\NTeddy, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很好\NYeah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小泰\NTeddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟我可以说实话\NIt's me you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}孩子没了\NWe lost the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托妮流产了\NTawney miscarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天哪  太遗憾了  亲爱的\NOh, my God. I'm so sorry, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}医生说  这很正常\NThe doctor said, uh, it's nature's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}知道吗\NYou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这种事很常见\NThese things are pretty common.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比大家想的还要常见\NHappen more often than people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实如此\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但还是挺可惜的\NBut, still, that's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实\NIt is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托妮还好吗\NHow's Tawney dealing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个真的不好说\NIt's hard to tell, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然了\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在她心情一定很复杂\NThings must be so complicated for her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来  亲爱的\NCome here, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我完全支持你  桑德拉\NYou have my full support, now, Sondra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想让你知道这点\NI want you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这对我意义重大  议员\NThat means a lot, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还以为霍顿不会同意流放\NI wasn't sure Holden would go for banishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说的话一定很有说服力\NYou must've been very persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他还没签字\NWell, he hasn't signed off on it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果不签  你用撤销保释威胁他了吗\NDid you threaten to revoke his bond if he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真的会撤销吗\NWould you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我当然会考虑这么做\NI would certainly consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}明白了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}哪位法官来签发他的认罪协议\NAnd what judge will sign off on this plea deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}凯尔特法官\NJudge Kelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要担心吗\NShould I worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说实话  你得时刻注意  桑德拉\NWell, you should always worry, Sondra, generally speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但尤其是这位马库斯·凯尔特法官\NBut especially with the honorable Marcus Kelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个案子在某些方面\NHe'll need some hand-holding
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你得跟他说清楚...\Non certain aspects of this case --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}首先  为什么撤掉强奸指控\NWhy you dropped the rape charge, for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有精样  没有目击证人\NNo sperm, no witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但他还是会要细节  具体细节\NHe'll still want details -- specific details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么意思\NMeaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}盘问霍顿\NHave Holden debrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让他回想谋杀案发生的那一夜\NHave him walk us through the night of the murder --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让他重新说一遍\NHis latest version.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道盘问是什么\NI know what a debrief is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样凯尔特问起\NThat way, when Kelter asks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么不起诉霍顿强奸汉娜时\Nwhy you didn't charge Holden with Hanna's rape,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就可以把重点转移到那句\Nyou can point to the transcript where it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"我杀了她  我没强奸她"上了\N"I killed her -- I didn't rape her."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那他也得这样说啊\NIf he says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他签掉协议就好了\NIt would just be better if he signs the confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他最好这么说\NHe better say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果他不愿意坦白\NWhat's the point of his plea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那认罪有什么意义\Nif he's not willing to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不就是为了让他坦白一切吗\NIsn't that what this is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在增加要求有点晚了  罗兰\NIt's a little late in the game to add demands, Roland --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}尤其是再盘问他\NEspecially a debrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想听他亲口承认\NI want to hear it from the horse's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想让别人说\NI don't want there to be any talk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个认罪协议只是为了我们的面子\Nthat this was a-a plea deal to save face on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你呢\NDo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然不想\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是觉得\NI-I just can't imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}斯特恩先生不会允许自己的委托人经历那种事\Nthat Mr. Stern would allow his client to go through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}经历什么\NThrough what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最后一次承认自己杀了人的羞耻感吗\NThe humiliation of having to answer for his actions once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得凯尔特法官\NI can't imagine judge Kelter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在没有盘问的情况下不会签发协议\Nsigning off on a plea agreement without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实  我可以保证他不会签发\NIn fact, I can guarantee you he won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一定要盘问他  桑德拉\NGet the debrief, Sondra,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}否则你的一切努力都要打水漂了\Nor all your good work will likely be for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}乔治\NGeorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好  乔治\NHello! George!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人在家吗\NAnybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}乔治\NGeorge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亲爱的乔治  我来看你了\N把你家的墙弄坏了  抱歉\N丹尼尔·霍顿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丹尼尔  听我说\NDaniel, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要求重新盘问证实了我们以前的想法\NAsking for the debrief affirms what we already knew --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们根本不知道那晚发生了什么事\NThey really have no idea what happened that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在他们想让你帮他们捋清事情的经过\NNow they're asking you to fill in the blanks for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我随便编点说说可以吗\NIs it all right if I just make something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果他们想立案起诉你\NIf they want to build a case against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就让他们从头开始吧\Nlet them start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从头  我已经认罪了\NScratch? I confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个我会帮你搞定的\NI'll get it thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的吗  乔恩\NWill you really, Jon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这次跟第一次审判不一样  丹尼尔\NThis wouldn't be like your first trial, Daniel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果再次审判的话\Nif it came to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你现在拥有\NYou would have resources
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当时你们家人没有的资源\Nyour family didn't have back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}司法部很重视这案子\NJustice row is all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}即使他们真的撤销你的保释\NLook, even if they did revoke your bond,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们也可以申请电子监控什么的\Nwe would push for some sort of electronic monitoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你顶多也就被关个一两天\NYou wouldn't be in custody for more than a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后就可以回家了\NThen you could go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那到场的会有谁\NSo, who would be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么到场\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}审讯盘问的时候\NAt the debrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现任检察官和前任检察官\NThe current prosecutor and the former.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}福克斯先生\NMr. Foulkes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  福克斯先生\NYes -- Mr. Foulkes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能警长也会到场\NAnd probably the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都是老朋友了\NOld friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丹尼尔  你不该接受协议\NDaniel, you shouldn't take the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你已经说过了  乔恩\NYou've said that already, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}向你传达他们提出的条件是我的职责\NIt was my duty to communicate their offer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我非常明确地告诉你  如果再次上庭\NBut it is also my duty to tell you in the strongest terms
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道我们能赢\Nthat if we went to trial, I know we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会考虑你的提议\NI will take your counsel under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}与此同时  好好处理认罪协议的事\NIn the meantime, move ahead with the deal --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}包括重新审讯盘问\Ndebrief included.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早弄早好\NThe sooner, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么这么做  丹尼尔\NWhy are you doing this, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很简单\NIt's not complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只想让这件事快点结束  乔恩\NI just want it to be over, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不想吗\NDon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想这样结束\NNot this way, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人不会总是如愿以偿\NCan't always get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你最近见过住18号的乔治·梅尔顿吗\NYou seen George Melton lately, over in number 18?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看到你们家门前有摄像头\NI saw you have security cameras on the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那些...\NAre those --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是真的吗  是真的\NReal? Yeah, they real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且大部分时间可以正常使用\NWork, too -- mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你点击菜单\NYou click up to the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就可以看到具体日期\NThat lets you look at the specific days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后可以快进快退\NAnd you can toggle up and down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  我知道了  谢谢\NAll right, I'll figure it out. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}乔治亚州的警长在这里都有管辖权吗\NI didn't know Georgia sheriffs had jurisdiction down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是以警长的身份来的\NI'm here unofficially.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不到万不得已我可不想招惹是非\NDon't want to poke the snake 'less I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这我没意见\NI don't have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}明天见\NSee y'all tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亲爱的\NWell, hey, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不用今天就把账本送过来的\NYou didn't have to bring the books by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}反正我也得去杂货店买点东西\NWell, I have to pick up some things at the grocery store,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以...\Nso...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个月业绩不错\NWe had a pretty good month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我感觉应该比上几个月好点\NI thought it might've been a little bit better than the last few.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看看这些轮辋\NLook at all the rims.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他做得太棒了\NHe's done such a great job with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实不错\NIt's pretty impressive, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得因为他来买轮胎的人好像也多了\NI think he's even brought in a few more tire customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是双赢\NIt's a win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我喜欢这个\NI like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我应该找他租来用用\NI think I might try to work out a deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}珍妮特\NJanet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有些消息\NI've got some news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我真的不想告诉你\NI really don't want to have to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他来家里了\NHe came by the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小泰\NTeddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他告诉你了吗\NHe told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我了\NHe did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这种事常有  泰德\NIt happens, Ted --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比人们以为的还要经常发生\Nmore often than people realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要流产的话还是早点为好\NIt's better to have an early miscarriage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总比孩子大了强\Nthan a late one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怀丹尼尔之前我就流过一次\NI had one before Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还记得我告诉过你吗\NRemember I told you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然记得\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托妮年轻坚强  他们会熬过去的\NTawney's young and strong. They'll get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然了\NI'm sure they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过我还是有点震惊\NStill... a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很遗憾  泰德\NI'm sorry, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总有一天你会当爷爷的\NYou'll be a granddaddy someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}霍顿  你有来访者\NHolden. You've got a visiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是谁啊\NWho is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}妈妈让我代她问好\NMother sends her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以为咱俩不见面会好点\NI thought it'd be easier for us not to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但实际上  并非如此\NBut it's... not easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}并非如此\NIt's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}煤气公司干得怎么样\NHow's the gas company?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我升职了\NThey promoted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吗\NThey did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}高级客服专家\NSenior customer-service specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也有自己的单间了\NGot my own cubicle and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}像我一样\NJust like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望你能回大学学习\NI wish you'd go on back to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但事情总有个先后\NFirst things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有好消息告诉你  丹尼尔\NGot some good news, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}司法部要派一个新律师来为你辩护\NJustice row is sending down a new guy to represent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们把一切都押上了\NThey are all-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真好\NWell, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会救你出来的  丹尼\NWe're gonna get you out of here, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想玩猜字游戏[刽子手]吗\NWant to play hangman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}猜字游戏\NHangman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不合适吗\NInappropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}正相反  你先吧\NThe opposite. You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}10个字母\N10 letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}里面有R吗\NIs there an "R"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是你的脑袋\NIt's your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这可不是好兆头啊\NNot looking good for our hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}L呢\N"L."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里有个L\NThere is an "L."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}干得漂亮\NNicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在我住在附近  我们每周都能一起玩\NNow that I'm nearby, we could do this every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那简直是个残忍而罕见的惩罚\NWell, that would be cruel and unusual punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有T吗\NHow about a "T"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对谁残忍啊\NCruel for who?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对你  妹妹\NYou, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}正相反呢  哥哥\NQuite the opposite, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天啊\NMy god.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我确实没想到会发展成这样\NI sure didn't think it would turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你得跟他谈谈  阿曼莎  要不就成真了\NYou have to talk to him, Amantha, or it's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我已经试过了  乔恩\NI already tried, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可我们不能就这么放弃啊\NWe can't just give up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一直在想你第一次出现\NI've been thinking about that first time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谈起案子的时候\Nthat you came down to talk about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你无法想象你给我们带来了多大的希望\NYou can't imagine the hope that you gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是在完成我的工作\NJust trying to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不管丹尼尔做了什么决定\NNo matter what Daniel decides to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}希望你都不要怪自己\NI don't want you to blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}妈妈是对的\NMother's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}毕竟  这是他的生活\NAt the end of the day, it's his life --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就像我的生活是我的  你的也属于你一样\Njust like it's my life, and just like it's your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都得为自己的决定\NWe all have to deal with the consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}承担后果\Nof our decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还没结束  阿曼莎\NIt's not over, Amantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道\NI know it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但不管怎样\NBut regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得你应该接受波士顿的工作\NI think you should take that job in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么意思\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会跟你去了  乔恩\NI'm not coming with you, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是因为认罪协议的事\NIt's not because of the plea deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  是因为这事\NWell... it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.67,0:24:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但只是因为这件事\Nbut only in the way that it has forced me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}强迫我去想我的生活中除了丹尼尔\Nto think about what I would want in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真正想要的是什么\Noutside of all things Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那里面没有我吗\NAnd that doesn't include me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.93,0:24:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道  乔恩\NI don't know, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.38,0:24:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许有吧\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.58,0:24:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道我想要什么\NI don't know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.38,0:24:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只知道我过去想要的是什么\NI only know what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.40,0:24:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我懂了\NI hear you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且我也理解你的想法  阿曼莎\Nand I understand where you're coming from, Amantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.06,0:24:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的\NI really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我不会放弃我们俩的爱情的\NBut I'm not giving up on us --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.86,0:24:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就像我不会放弃丹尼尔的事一样\Nany more than I'm giving up on Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.87,0:24:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是怕\NI just wonder if we won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.02,0:25:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们总会让对方想起\Nsomehow always remind each other
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.78,0:25:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这件倒霉的悲剧\Nof this whole goddamn tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.48,0:25:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比如一些表情或者话语\NSome look or some word.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.21,0:25:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或是我们俩就是因为它才走到了一起的事实\NOr just because it's how we came together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.72,0:25:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还是等认罪协议的事解决了\NLet's just wait until this plea deal is resolved
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们再决定我们之间该怎么办吧\Nbefore we make any decisions one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.06,0:25:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好啊  乔恩\NSure, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.31,0:26:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快点  加布里尔  快点\NCome on, Gabriel! Faster, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.66,0:26:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}孩子们  等等  等等妈妈\NGuys, wait! Wait for mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.80,0:26:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}圣经
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.94,0:26:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好  泰德\NHello, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.26,0:26:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}妈妈呢\NWhere's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.80,0:26:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}楼上\NUpstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.36,0:26:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你有什么心事  泰德\NWhat's on your mind, Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.49,0:26:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人不该听信一面之词  丹尼尔\NThere's two sides to every story, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.95,0:26:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得这话很对\NI've learned that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.73,0:27:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也知道小泰不是完人\NAnd I know Teddy's no angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.35,0:27:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我完全无法理解\NBut I cannot for the life of me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.40,0:27:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你到底是以什么样的心境\Nunderstand what your side of the story would be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.80,0:27:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能对他做出那样的事\Nto cause you to do what you did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.07,0:27:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}除非这事不是真的\NUnless it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.58,0:27:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是真的  泰德\NIt's no lie, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.92,0:27:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我确实那么做了\NI'm guilty as charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.99,0:27:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你告诉我  我们该怎么办  丹尼尔\NThen tell me how we make this right, Daniel,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.07,0:27:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们怎样才能维持这个家\Nhow we exist as a family now --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.83,0:27:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们要怎么告诉你妈妈\Nhow we even tell your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉他妈妈什么\NTell your mother what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}出什么事了\NWhat's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.16,0:27:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有事要告诉你  妈妈\NThere's something I have to tell you, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.31,0:27:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切都会好的  泰德\NEverything's gonna be okay, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.07,0:27:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么会好的\NWhat is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.88,0:27:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我接受认罪协议\NI'm taking the plea deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.09,0:27:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但其中有一条\NBut one of the stipulations is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.52,0:27:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得离开波利\NI have to leave Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.54,0:28:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实是得离开这个州\NThe entire state, essentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.66,0:28:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要多久\NFor how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.56,0:28:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}嗯\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}永远吧\Nforever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.62,0:28:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得关门了  警长\NI need to close up, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.39,0:28:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再等几分钟  行吗\NJust a couple more minutes, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.59,0:28:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}搞什么\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.33,0:29:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大日子吧\NBig day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.40,0:29:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}开始有这种感觉了\NIt's beginning to feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.65,0:29:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你告诉妈妈被驱逐的事了\NSo, you told mom about the banishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.29,0:29:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.30,0:29:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那盘问的事呢\NAnd the debrief?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉她有什么意义呢\NWhat would've been the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}离开时良心好受些吧\NWalk away with a clear conscience, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.55,0:29:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果这是你的目的\NIf that's your aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.39,0:29:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是来劝你改主意的  丹尼尔\NI'm not here to change your mind, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.26,0:29:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以你不用担心\NSo you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.73,0:29:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}乔恩是想让我试试的\NJon wanted me to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.31,0:29:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}乔恩啊\NDear jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你来干什么\NThen why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.99,0:29:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你这么做之后\N'cause after you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.99,0:29:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也将不再是从前的我了\NI'm not gonna be the same person anymore, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我想再当一次之前的我\NI wanted to be this person with you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.97,0:29:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你要成为什么人\NWho are you gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.54,0:29:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.22,0:30:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望不是个讨人厌的人\NI hope it won't be a bitter person.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.07,0:30:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也希望\NMe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.57,0:30:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不想被免罪  是吗\NYou don't want to be exonerated, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.11,0:30:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不只是想救你出狱  丹尼尔\NI didn't just want to get you out, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.47,0:30:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望能为你正名  为我们正名\NI wanted to clear your name -- our name.
