Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.84,0:45:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起初我的确是记不得了  但\NWell, a-at first, I-I didn't, but...
