Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.77,0:46:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能细节不清楚\NMaybe the details were foggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.27,0:46:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但事实很清楚\Nbut the truth was as clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.42,0:46:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在也是如此\NIt remains so.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.97,0:46:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说了我可以回家\NYou said I could go home.
