Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.31,0:46:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们没有\NThey didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.71,0:46:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她怎么死的  丹尼尔\NHow did she die, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.24,0:47:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丹尼尔\NDaniel.
