Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.02,0:47:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到她死\NUntil she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.91,0:47:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我杀了她\NI killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.27,0:47:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没人逼你这么说\NAnd no one put words in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.49,0:47:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没人逼你承认\NNo one coerced your confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.27,0:47:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对吧\NDid they?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.41,0:47:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.90,0:47:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们没有\NThey didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.73,0:48:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们完事了吗\NAre we done?
