Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.55,0:48:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}记忆涌现\NMemories.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.83,0:48:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你该坐坐\Nyou should sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.11,0:48:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能要等一会他们才会把认罪协议呈给法官\NIt might be a while before we present the plea to the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.11,0:48:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我坐了好几个小时了\NI've been sitting for hours.
