Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.53,0:51:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这就是它吸引人的地方吧\NYou might say that's one of its attractions.
